## 📂 Datasets

Below is the complete data dictionary for all tables used in this Healthcare Analytics project.

---

## 🏥 Encounters

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| Id | Primary Key. Unique identifier of the encounter. |
| Start | Date & time the encounter started (ISO8601 UTC). |
| Stop | Date & time the encounter ended (ISO8601 UTC). |
| Patient | Foreign key to the Patient table. |
| Organization | Foreign key to the Organization table. |
| Payer | Foreign key to the Payer table. |
| EncounterClass | Encounter type: ambulatory, emergency, inpatient, wellness, urgentcare. |
| Code | Encounter code from SNOMED‑CT. |
| Description | Description of the encounter type. |
| Base_Encounter_Cost | Base cost excluding procedures, meds, immunizations, etc. |
| Total_Claim_Cost | Total cost including all line items. |
| Payer_Coverage | Amount covered by the payer. |
| ReasonCode | Diagnosis code (SNOMED‑CT) if encounter targeted a condition. |
| ReasonDescription | Description of the reason code. |

