## 🩺 Procedures

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| Start | Date & time procedure started (ISO8601 UTC). |
| Stop | Date & time procedure ended (ISO8601 UTC). |
| Patient | Foreign key to the Patient table. |
| Encounter | Foreign key to the Encounter table. |
| Code | Procedure code (SNOMED‑CT). |
| Description | Description of the procedure. |
| Base_Cost | Line‑item cost of the procedure. |
| ReasonCode | Diagnosis code (SNOMED‑CT) for why the procedure was performed. |
| ReasonDescription | Description of the reason code. |
